# FILE: studentDashboard/marketplaceLedger/orderHistory.desc
# ROLE: Physical Goods & Store Transaction Tracker
# ROUTE: /dashboard/orders
# ACCOUNT: Student only
# THEME: Dark · e-commerce log · amber alerts · status pills

## 1. PENDING ACTION NOTIFIER (Top Fold)
- SHOWN ONLY: if there's an order awaiting ShamCash receipt upload
- CARD STYLE: border-[#F59E0B]/30 · bg-[#F59E0B]/5 · rounded-2xl (amber alert)
- MESSAGE: "الطلب #HS-702 ينتظر إيصال الدفع — يُرجى الرفع الآن"
- ACTION: [📤 رفع الإيصال] → simplified payment form

## 2. MASTER ORDER TIMELINE
- LIST STYLE: vertical stack of order rows · bg-[#0F1828] · rounded-2xl · border
- COLUMNS:
  - ORDER ID: "#HS-702" — monospace
  - ITEM: small thumbnail + product name
  - STATUS PILLS:
    - 🕒 قيد الانتظار — muted amber
    - 💳 مدفوع — emerald
    - 🚚 جاهز للاستلام — indigo
    - ✅ مُستلم — gray (closed)
  - PRICE: "450,000 SYP"

## 3. PICKUP NODE INSTRUCTIONS (Active Order)
- BORDERED BOX: shows location + broker name
- SECURE PICKUP CODE: 4-digit PIN (shown to student · broker enters it to confirm pickup)
- Location example: "مبنى هندسة المعلوماتية — الطابق 2 — مكتب 402"

## 4. SAVINGS COUNTER
- CARD: "وفّرت إجمالاً 155,000 SYP مقارنة بأسعار السوق"
- TEXT: emerald gradient-text value

## 5. ACTIONS
- [🔄 شراء مجدداً] for consumables
- [⚠️ مشكلة في الطلب؟] → admin dispute modal
